                <p>The Gulf <img class="du1" src="img/du1.gif"> (2 August 1990 – 28 February 1991), codenamed Operation <img class="desert" src="img/desert.gif">  <img class="shield" src="img/shield.gif">  (2 August 1990 – 17 January 1991) for operations leading to the buildup of troops and defense of Saudi Arabia and Operation <img src="img/desert2.gif"> Storm (17 January 1991 – 28 February 1991) in its <img class="army2" src="img/army2.gif"> phase, was a <img class="du1" src="img/du1.gif"> waged by coalition forces from 35 nations led by the United States against Iraq in response to Iraq's <img class="army2" src="img/army2.gif"> and annexation of Kuwait.</p>
